signatureAbility.signatureDescription: Defenders with this ability use faster run shed moves for a better chance at shedding blocks against outside zone plays.
Defenders with this ability have a greater chance of forcing fumbles when landing Perfect Hit Sticks
Players with this ability have a chance to replenish their stamina, once per play, when it is half depleted
Ballcarriers with this ability have an increased chance to break the first tackle attempt on kick returns
Blockers with this ability will frequently attempt and win impact blocks against linebackers and defensive backs when playing as a lineman or fullback.
Blockers with this ability are almost guaranteed to win any double team block they are engaged in
Blockers with this ability will frequently attempt and win impact blocks against linebackers and defensive backs when playing as a lineman or fullback.

signatureAbility.signatureActivationDescription: Make consecutive passes for 5+ yards in air
signatureAbility.signatureDescription: The best quarterbacks learn to take calculated risks. When they enter the zone, they can't be intercepted (by AI defenders) and have increased throw speed.
Passers with this ability have perfect accuracy on all unpressured throws while their feet are set in the pocket (except on high/low throws).
Passers with this ability have faster passing animations when they are throwing under pressure
Ballcarriers with this ability have more powerful truck animations and a larger timing window for perfect trucks.
